snippet.textDisplay:
I will admit when their relationship started I was a "doubter". I thought it was a "fling" or "rebound".... But as I've watched them evolve over the years. Gwen is good for Blake and Blake is good for Gwen.
I was so sad to see Miranda gone cause I really believed they were the perfect match but we NEVER seen the love between Miranda and Blake that we see with Gwen and Blake. There is DEFINITELY more flame with the 2 of them than there ever was with Blake and Miranda. Miranda was cold compared to Gwen. Anyway... I LOVE IT! And I hope that Gwen and Blake have MANY happy years together! They both deserve it!
